title: ACE_LIGHTNING_01.avi
description: Ace Lightning episode 01, "The Game Begins". Thirteen-year-old Mark Hollander has just moved from England to America, and when lightning strikes his videogame during a storm, an entire cast of superheroes and villains appear. Mark now has to adjust to his new country, meet new people, and help hero Ace Lightning save the world from Lord Fear--one high school student&#039;s social-life-destroying event at a time.
